data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Atlantic Commons, Delray Beach! This stunning 2-story single-family residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms with a thoughtful split-bedroom design, providing privacy and comfort for the whole family.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan seamlessly connecting the living room, dining area, and a modern kitchen. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring granite countertops, contemporary appliances, and a convenient kitchen island for both culinary creations and casual gatherings. The living room, adorned with ample natural light, opens up to the patio through sliding doors, offering a perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living. Picture yourself sipping morning coffee or entertaining friends while enjoying the serene views of the lake from your private patio.

Venture upstairs to discover a spacious family room, providing an additional space for relaxation and entertainment. The master bedroom, also located on the second floor, offers a retreat-like experience with a generous walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom complete with a soothing tub.

This residence is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Take advantage of the well-maintained community's resort-style amenities, adding an extra layer of luxury to your daily life. Whether it's a refreshing dip in the pool, a workout in the fitness center, or a leisurely stroll through manicured grounds, Atlantic Commons has it all.

Convenience is key, and this home is just minutes away from fine shopping, dining, and all the vibrant attractions Delray Beach has to offer. Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional property in a community that combines comfort, style, and the best of South Florida living. Schedule your showing today and make this house your new home!
